Package: sparseshootS
Title: Sparse Shooting S-Estimator for Robust High-Dimensional Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lea", "Bottmer", role = "aut"),
    person("Christophe", "Croux", role = "aut"),
    person("Ines", "Wilms", email = "i.wilms@maastrichtuniversity.nl",
           role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: Computes the sparse shooting S-estimator and the shooting
    S-estimator for robust regression in high-dimensional settings with
    cellwise outliers. Implements the method described in Bottmer, Croux,
    and Wilms (2022), "Sparse regression for large data sets with outliers",
    Econometrics and Statistics.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Imports:
    pcaPP,
    Rcpp (>= 1.0.0),
    robustbase,
    robustHD,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
LinkingTo:
    Rcpp,
    RcppArmadillo
Config/roxygen2/version: 8.0.0
